## 5. Tag Adjacency Map

The recommendation engine uses tag adjacency for strategic exploration. When the visitor likes "metallic + cool", the engine probes "glossy + cool" or "metallic + neutral":

```
tiny ↔ small ↔ medium ↔ large ↔ monumental
low_poly ↔ medium_poly ↔ high_poly
cubic ↔ wide ↔ irregular ↔ tall
flat ↔ cubic, wide
dark ↔ cool ↔ neutral ↔ warm ↔ earth
matte ↔ rough
glossy ↔ matte
metallic → glossy
organic → rough, matte
glass → emissive, glossy
concrete → rough, matte
emissive → glossy
```

