## 12. Pipeline Commands Reference

### Export Portal models (run on PC with Blender installed):
```bash
blender --background --python batch_export.py -- --input "C:/path/to/source_blender_collection/portal/_models" --output "./exports/portal" --game portal
```

### Tag Portal models (run on PC with Blender installed):
```bash
blender --background --python auto_tagger_v2.py -- --input "C:/path/to/source_blender_collection/portal/_models" --output "./tags/portal.json" --game portal
```

### Build unified metadata:
```bash
python build_metadata.py --tags-dir ./tags --output ./metadata.json
```

### Repeat for other games:
Replace `portal` with `portal2`, `hl2`, `tf2` in the above commands.

